OL,3,CPoliticians vote for most of them to
OL,4,Cbe paid less
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have voted to
OL,7,Freduce most of their salaries due to
OL,8,Fthe island's difficult financial
OL,9,Fsituation.
OL,11,FEvery term an independent panel
OL,12,Freviews deputies' pay which is usually
OL,13,Faccepted without question.
OL,15,FHowever, the original plan to maintain
OL,16,Fthe base salary for politicians came
OL,17,Fbefore the States agreed to a heavily
OL,18,Freduced budget.
