OL,3,CPoliticians vote for most of them to
OL,4,Cbe paid less
OL,6,FThe Policy and Resources Committee
OL,7,Fsuggested reducing pay by 3%, with
OL,8,Famendments leading to a cut across
OL,9,Fmost roles from 1 July.
OL,11,FThe Chief Minister, Guernsey's highest-
OL,12,Fpaid political position, will take
OL,13,Fhome #82,229, a drop of around #2,500.
OL,15,FMembers of Policy and Resources and
OL,16,Fthe Presidents of most other
OL,17,Fcommittees will be paid #63,181.
