OL,3,CPoliticians vote for most of them to
OL,4,Cbe paid less
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Presidents of the
OL,7,FStates Assembly and Constitution
OL,8,FCommittee and Scrutiny Committee will
OL,9,Fsee the largest salary cut: from
OL,10,F#65,135 to #56,166.
OL,12,FThis will bring them in line with the
OL,13,FPresident of Development and Planning.
OL,15,FAll other deputies will see an
OL,16,Fincrease from #48,213 to #49,151.
OL,18,FThere are concerns from some that
OL,19,FGuernsey's high cost of living may
OL,20,Flimit people from wanting to begin a
OL,21,Fpolitical career.
