OL,3,CPoliticians vote for most of them to
OL,4,Cbe paid less
OL,6,FThis could impact diversity in the
OL,7,FStates, particularly given the next
OL,8,Felection will take place just before
OL,9,Fthe pay changes come into force.
OL,11,FDeputy Tina Bury says: "That warm
OL,12,Ffuzzy feeling you get from doing a
OL,13,Fpublic service doesn't pay your rent.
OL,15,F"You can't just have people in here
OL,16,Fwho have other business interests to
OL,17,Fkeep them afloat, because that is not
OL,18,Frepresentative of our population."
